data.description: Welcome home to this beautifully renovated 2 story home with finished basement in Deer Creek in Stone Mountain. Refinished hardwoods on the main floor, new interior paint, new carpet, a new HVAC just to name a few. This large home has 5 bedrooms, 4 on the second level and one in the basement. There are 3.5 baths, 2 on the second level, 1/2 on the main and one in the basement. There is a beautiful sun room off the gourmet kitchen with stainless steel appliances, that overlooks the backyard. A large storage area on the basement level is great for lawn equipment. Separate living room on the main level and large dining area with a 3 sided fireplace to keep you warm! Finished basement has a large room for maybe a large screen tv, wet bar, bedroom and full bath. Don't miss this one!
